jobInfo.postDescription:
responsibilities:
Car2x function test on bench and vehicle, responsible for the coordination of all testing activities of the Car-to-X function and its relevant functions, e.g. backend service, navigation and connectivity.
•Capability of taking FO role independently
•Organization and preparation of test drive
•Basic feature and acceptance test.
•Cross-application customer testing
•HMI validation for the respective application
•Documentation of defects
•Verification of fixed defects
•Maintenance and extension of test specifications
•Reporting and improvement suggestions of potential improvements
•Testing equipment maintenance
•Cross-department cooperation
qualifications:
•Candidate with C-V2X (head unit + TCU) bench/vehicle test experience is preferred, including test bench setup, maintenance, operation on vehicle infotainment system (vehicle head unit, screen display)
•Basic knowledge of Vector CANoe with Vector products.
•Basic knowledge of in-vehicle testing, Linux system, diagnostics
•Profound knowledge of Windows system, Microsoft office software, including but not limited to excel, word, power point and outlook, confluence, SVN/Git and Jira.
•Basic Knowledge of C-V2X China standards
•Basic knowledge in Android ADB, QXDM/HIDS logger, DLT logger, BluePiraT/ETHOS logger, RS232/TTL logger, Wireshark.
•Educational background in Computer science, Electrical Engineering or Telecommunication
Self responsible working attitude
•Good communication and documentation skills
•English language skills in reading and writing for tickets and supplier communication is necessary.
jobInfo.address: 北京大兴区北京经济技术开发区亦庄

brandComInfo.introduce: 成立于2000年，瞬联是一家提供技术咨询、软件研发及行业级整体技术解决方案的专业服务供应商。瞬联在电信、嵌入式、IoT、汽车、移动互联网及企业软件方案等领域拥有超过20年的深厚研发经验。瞬联通过其优质的交付能力、灵活的合作模式和客户导向的理念赢得了许多世界500强企业客户，公司在大中华地区、美国、加拿大、欧洲的主要城市设有办公室和研发中心。近年来，瞬联11次被国际外包专业协会（IAOP）评为全球外包行业100强公司，同时也屡次得到Gartner、IDC和中国外包网等国内外机构的奖项和荣誉。瞬联拥有ISO9001和27001认证以及CMMI3证书（含敏捷开发流程）。
